#

Citrus-Glazed Roasted Turkey

210 min
$50
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%
Servings: 10

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Cuisine:

AmericanHoliday

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

TurkeyHolidayRoastedCitrus

Description

A succulent turkey roasted to perfection with a zesty citrus glaze that adds a refreshing twist to your holiday feast.

Ingredients

  • whole turkey: 1 (12-14 lbs)
  • orange juice: 1 cup
  • lemon juice: 1/4 cup
  • honey: 1/2 cup
  • garlic cloves, minced: 4
  • olive oil: 1/4 cup
  • salt: 2 teaspoons
  • black pepper: 1 teaspoon
  • fresh herbs (thyme, rosemary, or sage): 1/4 cup
  • butter, melted: 1/2 cup
